dc_title_s: Transit Stops - Itinerary Stops Only - Change Log: Minnesota
dc_description_s: The Transit Stops Change Log layer contains over 14,000 active and inactive transit stops that are part of a transit route itinerary in the Twin Cities seven county metropolitan area. The layer flags when a stop is removed or added from pattern itineraries.  The dataset includes attributes from the primary transit stop database maintained for MetroTransit and for customer information for other transit provider transit services. The locations are mapped referencing NCompass Technologies Inc. street centerline network along with streets generated internally at MetroTransit.
